{"tid":1488962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"分化夠未","createTime":"2019-08-19T17:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T01:07:49.000Z","uid":218801,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a53c616beae3b315bef3160e0aed3b0a8d330f70","tid":1488962,"uid":218801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:58:32.000Z","msg":"我係一個前線 今日都有去維園<br />\n咩左膠 嘉年華會 我屌你地講撚完未？<br />\n今日又唔係有咩光復行動 or 遊行<br />\n唔通真係玩下都唔比？ 講真,6月以嚟<br />\n得尖沙咀觀星活動 同今日維園活動先至可以令我暫時忘記煩惱 <br />\n可以開心一下<br />\n<br />\n唔通要日日都作戰狀態？<br />\n女義士中槍，有人被打至腦血岀，700名手足被捕<br />\n我全部都無忘記<br />\n依個仇我地一定會報<br />\n<br />\n大佬阿 精神狀態都好重要 <br />\n適當放鬆都必需<br />\n我地已經失去左6名手足<br />\n日日情況都咁緊張<br />\n你頂得住 我都頂唔住啦<br />\n<br />\n我地好多人都係學生<br />\n我地今個暑假已經比曬依場運動<br />\n街站 派傳單 發夢<br />\n比我地開心一下姐<br />\n唔洗下下屌我地嘅<br />\n他們還青春，還他們青春<br />\n比返一日青春我地 已經係我地悲微嘅請求<br />\n<br />\n而且今日維園一路都有叫 光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n放心，瞓醒大家都會推返行動post"},{"pid":"4cb4b386fbdfdefb4f9547ad1a9143028a9a133e","tid":1488962,"uid":218801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:59:08.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"2b097ac9c84d7f72a471fae3813a0ee2ef809b1b","tid":1488962,"uid":218801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:59:18.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"6aeb6abeb1afaa488da01f0e6432912cb52c91dc","tid":1488962,"uid":218801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:00:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1358fe4fb342b360501607fdf148c7bc574ed2b1","tid":1488962,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:05:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>Fight for freedom<br />\nStand with Hong Kong</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n612 721 811<br />\n<br />\n821/823/831 死線（未定好）<br />\n<br />\n823人鏈<br />\n<br />\n824 去完觀塘再入機場<br />\n<br />\n825 荃葵青<br />\n<br />\n831 中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n9月三罷<br />\n<br />\n不分和勇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"a7856d3dc280298a354417858fa27bdfb9fe0ce9","tid":1488962,"uid":218801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"開心下姐，唔會影衰成個運動嘅"},{"pid":"dc2b342513d5f71f52e21881b3adc12d5df0b005","tid":1488962,"uid":218801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:23:55.000Z","msg":"唔好再屌啦"},{"pid":"87076f8093d5e5f500c923a7aa287b6403c23941","tid":1488962,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:26:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">824和理非自發出機場</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">錫政府春袋 癱瘓機場貨運</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">機鐵會有阻塞運動<br />\n需要車手去機場塞路<br />\n亦可以排隊入機場</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">記住善待遊客 盡幫佢地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTQBGjH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTQBGjH.jpg&h=a4cec47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7FesZK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS7FesZK.jpg&h=04f6b24b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0EG9gS5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0EG9gS5.jpg&h=fcdfc691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6eae219c2bd58c382b5d68ac20ff66402ebbba90","tid":1488962,"uid":266986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:28:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d1deafdd7e23385c238404523a70b5be065d496","tid":1488962,"uid":218801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:34:18.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"d6574bb6ea7b4cf0215fce64a85f82899970257a","tid":1488962,"uid":173191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:34:35.000Z","msg":"愛之深 責之切 百屌成材<br />\n<br />\n找數巴打單野我覺得無問題<br />\n個情況就等同尖沙咀果晚觀星活動<br />\n偶然輕鬆一下我覺得OK <br />\n其實入面啲巴絲都時不時嗌口號 <br />\n<br />\n但Follow隻狗閪真係要鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗌緊黑警但轉頭鳩衝去follow隻狗閪<br />\n點對得住啲受傷康復緊<br />\n審訊緊甚至犧牲咗嘅手足呢？<br />\n<br />\n好好諗清楚 然後做文宣準備吓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ebb427940a3cd12012c498a8e15c15d6825bb4e","tid":1488962,"uid":180606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:07:49.000Z","msg":"女義士好啲未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}